&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Describes disk-related information and optimization suggestions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;view-disk&#34;&gt;View disk&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#view-disk&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click the &lt;code&gt;Disk&lt;/code&gt; menu on the left menu bar of the platform to display the disk page, as shown in the figure below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/user-guide/disk/disk1_hu586b962710831052bb190f8f2f84d234_70715_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;291&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


disk page
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Disk pages are divided into 3 areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cluster selection area&lt;/strong&gt;: Select the corresponding cluster.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Query area&lt;/strong&gt;: Query the corresponding disk by disk ID, instance ID and node name.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;List area&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays disks, instances, usage and operation columns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The disk page after selecting the cluster is as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/user-guide/disk/disk2_huc4f6d93e34b39afdead8fc69986df97a_186869_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;443&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Disk page-select cluster
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The list area display is divided into 4 columns:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disk column&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays the disk ID, device name and creation time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Owner Column&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays the department, group and specific personnel of the node owner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instance column&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays the node ID, node name and region where the disk is located.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Usage column&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays disk capacity, maximum utilization, average utilization and last update time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operation Bar&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays the corresponding operations on the disk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;adjust-disk&#34;&gt;Adjust disk&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#adjust-disk&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click the &lt;code&gt;Adjust&lt;/code&gt; link to open the Adjust Disk Size dialog box, which displays detailed disk adjustment information and recommended adjustment plans, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;//localhost:1313/docs/user-guide/disk/disk3_huc497cd330fcd67249832763c798ad846_88237_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;387&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


adjust disk page
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;


